Interface NavigationBar

All Superinterfaces:
org.nasdanika.common.Adaptable, BootstrapElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HtmlElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.Marked, org.nasdanika.persistence.Marked, org.nasdanika.ncore.ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PagePart
All Known Implementing Classes:
NavigationBarImpl
public interface NavigationBar extends PagePart
A representation of the model object 'Navigation Bar'. Navigation bar has a brand and navigation items.

The following features are supported:

  • Brand
  • Dark
  • Expand
  • Background
See Also:
  • AppPackage.getNavigationBar()
